{"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/feats/feats.webp","name":"Tactician Dedication","system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You become trained in Warfare Lore; if you were already trained in Warfare Lore, you become trained in a skill of your choice. You gain the Ambush Tactics skill feat, even if you don't meet the skill feat's requirements.</p>\n<p>Choose a @Compendium[axerwans-tactician-class-pf2e.tactician-features.bZ23AYw3GMsFZdzE]{Paradigm} that corresponds to the ability you used to qualify for the archetype. You can use that ability modifier on Warfare Lore checks instead of Intelligence, and you have that paradigm for all purposes, but you don’t gain any of the other abilities it grants. You become trained in tactician class DC. You can't use gambit actions.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Special</strong> You can't select another dedication feat until you have gained two other feats from the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.journals.vx5FGEG34AxI2dow.JournalEntryPage.k9Ebp52kt0ZLHtMl]{Swashbuckler} archetype.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Axerwan's Tactician Class"},"rules":[{"key":"GrantItem","allowDuplicate":false,"uuid":"Compendium.axerwans-tactician-class-pf2e.tactician-features.bZ23AYw3GMsFZdzE"},{"key":"GrantItem","allowDuplicate":false,"uuid":"Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.knrawm4bMbDL9XS3"},{"adjustName":false,"choices":[{"label":"PF2E.AbilityInt","value":"int"},{"label":"PF2E.AbilityWis","value":"wis"},{"label":"PF2E.AbilityCha","value":"cha"}],"flag":"keyAbility","key":"ChoiceSet","prompt":"PF2E.SpecificRule.Prompt.ClassDCAbilityScore"},{"key":"ActiveEffectLike","mode":"override","path":"system.proficiencies.classDCs.tactician","priority":39,"value":{"ability":"{item|flags.pf2e.rulesSelections.keyAbility}","label":"Tactician","rank":1}}],"slug":"tactician-dedication","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":2},"traits":{"value":["archetype","dedication","multiclass"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionTy